{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take on your Grandpa's old shop and fix up your customer's treasured belongings. From bells to binoculars and toys to teapots, each forest friend will have something new for you to repair!\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179050/extras/steamgif2.gif?t=1740399251\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">To-Do List:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Piece together antiques, heirlooms, and favourite mugs for your customers, each with its own puzzle!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grow berries in your back garden to mix up into colourful paints, and paint up a storm</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your creations with a splash of colour, then sell them for a profit</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Keep your shop in check by cleaning up the floor, keeping the fire lit and the cookie jar full</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make your shop your own by picking out furniture, rugs and more!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179050/extras/steamgif1.gif?t=1740399251\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your shop with different colours and materials, grow plants and mix paint, spruce up the items that pass through the store, bake cookies for your neighbours, and listen to the latest gossip - are you ready to roll up your sleeves and open up shop?</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3179050?t=1740399251","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3179050?t=1740399251","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179050/02077c970c48907ed523043734ed991df29f28d7/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740399251","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai